C'hoari ChangeLog

Legend:
=======
+ New feature added or made an existing one better
- Removed a feature, or something bad happened
* Fixed a bug
! Changed something important, probably incompatibly.


0.1.0 - [2011.07.26]
	+ add simple curses interface
	+ add pages per games (type :<game> ; e.g. :q3)
	+ add help display (type :h or :help)
	+ add refresh command (type :e)
	+ add quit command (type :q or :quit or q or Q)
